data.description:
Fabulous 4 Bedroom / 3 bathroom home in a great neighborhood in Olive Branch.  This home features an Open concept Split floor plan and sits on a corner lot!
There are wood floors through out the main living areas except for the the tile in the bathrooms and kitchen !  There are 3 bedrooms on the main level!  Primary bedroom is separated from the other 2 bedrooms!  There are French doors leading out to the patio in the Primary bedroom and Living room. There are so many upgrades in this home! Beautiful updated light fixtures throughout the home and an amazing custom built wall unit with an electric fireplace in the Living room to cozy up to when it gets cold! Granite in the kitchen as well as stainless steel appliances to include the fridge which will remain with the home! Upstairs is another bedroom with a walk in closet and a huge Bonus Room!! Plenty of storage in the walk in attic! Don't miss out!   Call today to schedule a showing!
